OL,3,CRelief for expectant parents as
OL,4,Cbirthing unit returns to Cumbrian
OL,5,CHospital
OL,7,FExpectant parents have welcomed the
OL,8,Freopening of a Kendal maternity unit,
OL,9,Fafter it closed for almost a year due
OL,10,Fto midwife shortages.
OL,12,FFull maternity services have resumed
OL,13,Fat Westmorland General Hospital's
OL,14,FHelme Chase birth unit, which were
OL,15,Fsuspended from April 2024, but
OL,16,Fconcerns remain for its long term
OL,17,Ffuture.
