OL,3,CRelief for expectant parents as
OL,4,Cbirthing unit returns to Cumbrian
OL,5,CHospital
OL,7,FThe closure of the unit meant
OL,8,Fexpectant parents were forced to
OL,9,Ftravel to Lancaster or Barrow for care
OL,10,Fduring their pregnancy and to give
OL,11,Fbirth.
OL,13,FFollowing a successful recruitment
OL,14,Fcampaign, birth services - including
OL,15,Fantenatal and postnatal services,
OL,16,Fantenatal education, vaccination
OL,17,Fclinics, ultrasound scanning and
OL,18,Fconsultant-led clinics - have resumed.
