OL,3,CRelief for expectant parents as
OL,4,Cbirthing unit returns to Cumbrian
OL,5,CHospital
OL,7,FUHMBT says they have put robust plans
OL,8,Fin place to ensure that there will
OL,9,Fcontinue to be 24-hour midwifery on-
OL,10,Fcall services for birth within the
OL,11,Funit and at home.
OL,13,FThe unit, which has more than 20
OL,14,Fmembers of staff, offers antenatal and
OL,15,Fpostnatal services, antenatal
OL,16,Feducation, vaccination clinics,
OL,17,Fultrasound scanning and consultant-led
OL,18,Fclinics.
