OL,3,CRelief for expectant parents as
OL,4,Cbirthing unit returns to Cumbrian
OL,5,CHospital
OL,7,FHelme Chase is a midwife-led unit,
OL,8,Fwhere patients can give 24 hours-a-
OL,9,Fday, seven days-a-week, supported by a
OL,10,Fmidwife. Midwife-led units are for
OL,11,Fpregnancies where it is unlikely that
OL,12,Fthere will be any serious
OL,13,Fcomplications.
OL,15,FThe unit differs from the South Lakes
OL,16,FBirth Centre at Furness General
OL,17,FHospital (FGH) in Barrow and at the
OL,18,FRoyal Lancaster Infirmary, which are
OL,19,Fboth consultant-led units.
