OL,3,CRelief for expectant parents as
OL,4,Cbirthing unit returns to Cumbrian
OL,5,CHospital
OL,7,FSamantha Connelly, midwife and Helme
OL,8,FChase Unit manager, said: "Helme Chase
OL,9,Fhas a real family feel and we pride
OL,10,Fourselves on providing safe,
OL,11,Fpersonalised care and support
OL,12,Fthroughout pregnancy, birth and beyond.
OL,14,F"We are delighted to be offering our
OL,15,Fmidwife-led unit at Kendal as a choice
OL,16,Fof place of birth for families."
